channel.description:
Still in training, made him around 13:45 saterday sept 10th.. (didnt do tut till 17:03 on sunday) Start of day one: [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img139.imageshack.us/img139/2149/doomsheytomopar1kj6.png[/img][/URL] Trying to get 40 attack atm, where should i train?
End of day one: [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img471.imageshack.us/img471/5262/doomsheytomopar2tn4.png[/img][/URL] If you cant see the text;it says "Sup mopar, where should i go? Like the autoerz?
Ending stats for day 2: *34 cmb* [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img183.imageshack.us/img183/3999/endingstatforday2zj8.png[/img][/URL]
~Pie
PS that deff lvl wasnt on perpos, i was on rune scim poking rats (LOL) and then i switched to range...Deff lvl :( :mad:
